Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • MyGIS.Game

  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    This is class that represents the game Field 1: ALF is an ArrayList that hold all of the Fruit in the Game Field 2: ALP is an ArrayList that hold all of the Packman in the Game Field 3: time is the amount of time it takes for all the Fruit to be eaten by the Packmen
